betterquesting:10.desc:8:
In this place, my powerlessness is absolute. 
I am back to my initial state, to my natural state, to my true state. Powerlessness.
I do not like to be like this, I do not like to know this.
And yet, I must know this, I must be like this.
That is how I know what must be done. What can be changed. What must be changed.
I am powerless now, but I do not have to be...
